Functional.Name: Functional

Marketing_Analytics.Desc: Marketing cookies are used to track visitors through websites. The goal is to display ads that are relevant and interesting to the individual user and therefore more valuable to third-party publishers and advertisers.

cookies.Name: _gat

cookies.Name: _gid

cookies.Name: _hjAbsoluteSessionInProgress

cookies.Name: _hjid
cookies.PurposeDescription: Sets a unique ID for the session. This allows the website to obtain data on visitor behaviour for statistical purposes.

cookies.Name: _hjIncludedInSessionSample
cookies.PurposeDescription: Registers data on visitors' website-behaviour. This is used for internal analysis and website optimization.

cookies.Name: test_cookie
cookies.PurposeDescription: Used to check if the user's browser supports cookies.

Advertising.Name: Advertising
Advertising.Desc: To personalize and measure the effectiveness of advertising on our site and other websites. For example, we may serve you a personalized ad based on the pages you visit on our site.

Essential.Name: Essential
Essential.Desc: We use browser cookies that are necessary for the site to work as intended. For example, we store your website data collection preferences so we can honor them if you return to our site. You can disable these cookies in your browser settings but if you do the site may not work as intended.

cookies.Name: m
